 this\nwork is a constructive realization of J. Hadamard's opinion that physically\nmeaningful problems are always well-posed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Oct 2006 12:53:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Dec 2006 13:09:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
